data.title: Cultivation license fees
data.excerpt: Cultivation license types are based on the type of production and lighting used and the number of plants grown or size of the canopy. View a breakdown of fees for each of the cultivation license types, including specialty cottage, specialty, small, medium, large, nursery, and processor.
